    value: 10.5281/zenodo.21265445
    description: >-
      All versions of the code. This is the concept DOI, and it is the concept
      DOI deliberately. A release-specific DOI is minted from the tag that
      contains this file, so a file inside the archive cannot name it without
      stating a number it could not know at the time it was written. Release
      v3.0 shipped with that bug and had to be superseded by v3.1. The concept
      DOI exists before the release and resolves to the latest one.
